
Radium:-
Radium is a set of tools to manage inline styles on React elements.
It gives you powerful styling capabilities without CSS.

Installing Radium package:- 
yarn add radium
# or
npm install --save radium

Features:-
->Conceptually simple extension of normal inline styles
->Browser state styles to support :hover, :focus, and :active
->Media queries
->Automatic vendor prefixing
->Keyframes animation helper
->ES6 class and createClass support

Media queries:-
media queries are a popular technique for delivering a tailored style sheet to desktops,
laptops, tablets, and mobile phones (such as iPhone and Android phones).

(*)Refer css.tricks for more details.